Class OpenLcbCanFrame

java.lang.Object
  org.openlcb.can.OpenLcbCanFrame
All Implemented Interfaces:
CanFrame
public class OpenLcbCanFrame
extends Object
implements CanFrame

Carry and work with a CAN frame in OpenLCB format. For definiton, see http://openlcb.sf.net/trunk/documents/can/index.html Bit 0 of the frame is in the 0x10000000 position.
